cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use DeepMapper, please cite the Scientific Reports article below."
title: DeepMapper
abstract: >-
  A pipeline that maps non-image, high-dimensional data into image-like structures
  with minimal processing so it can be analysed with CNNs (and other deep models),
  without dimension reduction, recovering weak signals that standard filtering discards.
authors:
